# Tests

## AutoDown-T1 Markdown Round-trip Serialization
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend

- [x] Plain paragraph round-trips identically
- [x] Headings (H1–H3) preserve level and text
- [x] Bold, italic, and strikethrough inline marks
- [x] Bullet and numbered lists
- [x] Code blocks with language hint
- [x] Blockquotes
- [x] Links with URL and title
- [x] Images with alt text and src
- [x] Horizontal rules
- [x] Task lists with checked/unchecked items
- [x] Tables with header and body rows

## AutoDown-T2 Table IAL Persistence
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend

- [x] Loading Markdown with IAL applies colwidth to table cells
- [x] Loading Markdown with IAL applies rowheight to table rows
- [x] Saving editor content appends IAL after each table block
- [x] IAL is omitted when all widths/heights are auto
- [x] `"auto"` in IAL maps to `null` in ProseMirror attributes
- [x] Multiple tables in one document each get their own IAL block
- [x] IAL does not interfere with standard Markdown rendering
